<h1>Request Data Deletion</h1>

<p>If you would like your SummitOne account and associated data deleted, you may submit a request by emailing us.</p>

<p>Please include the following information:</p>

<ul>
<li>Your SummitOne account email</li>
<li>The subject line: <strong>Data Deletion Request</strong></li>
</ul>

<p>Email your request to:</p>

<p><strong>your@email.com</strong></p>

<p>We will process deletion requests within 7 days.</p>

<p>If you simply wish to stop using SummitOne, you may also delete the app from your device.</p>

